      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "SUBJECT: Comments on Article in The NEW YORKER",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "1. A call was made to the Air Technical Intelligence Center,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "1330 this date, (Captain Ruppelt) regarding the attached article.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "2. ATIC did not in any way indicate to [REDACTED] that the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "FBI has an interest in flying saucers. Furthermore, Captain",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "Ruppelt stated that the FBI to his knowledge has never been called",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "upon to furnish reports on flying saucers. ATIC is under the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "impression that [REDACTED] made the story up or picked it up from",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "a magazine or newspaper article sometime back that definitely",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "was not associated with their organization.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "3. ATIC suggests that you check further with Mr. Al Chop,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "Office of Public Information, and perhaps he can supply you with",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "the information you have requested.",
      "status": "image_matched"
